Title: fy_standoff
Author: -[NP]- Xiuide
Email: noobpwnage247@gmail.com
Website: http://www.noob-pwnage.com

Filename:fy_standoff_finalv2.bsp
Filesize: 1.29 MB
Date Released: 14 May 2007

Credits: Myself for the map ^^ and all alpha/beta testers

Istallation Instructions: Place the map here:
Steam\steamapps\your_accountname\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps
And you shoud be able to run it on your server


Description: This is a fort type FY map. This map was made to have a "real" map feel to it, with its use of textures and props. There are three routes to the enemy base; head-on,sewer, or a ledge on the rockface. The materials act normal, so don't expect the thin metal bunkers to protect you THAT much :-P 

Bugs: I'm sure if you look well, there are some things I missed.

Comments: This is the first map I'm realeasing, Hope everyone enjoys it.


Required Items: Steam and Counter Strike: Source
